00:13:09.500 --> 00:13:14.300
With all my heart, Ipardon him.

288
00:13:14.300 --> 00:13:17.430
A god on earth thou art.

289
00:13:21.030 --> 00:13:25.330
But for our trustybrother-in-law and the abbot,

290
00:13:25.330 --> 00:13:27.470
with all the rest of thatconsorted crew,

291
00:13:27.470 --> 00:13:30.370
