302
00:14:08.500 --> 00:14:11.730
"Have I no friend will ridme of this living fear?"

303
00:14:12.830 --> 00:14:14.170
Was it not so?

304
00:14:14.170 --> 00:14:16.300
These were his very words.

305
00:14:16.300 --> 00:14:18.730
"Have I no friend?" quothhe.

306
00:14:19.930 --> 00:14:22.800
He spake it twice andurged it twice together,did he not?

307
00:14:22.800 --> 00:14:23.800
