428
00:23:06.900 --> 00:23:09.800
Patience is stale, and Iam weary of it.

429
00:23:09.800 --> 00:23:10.800
Help!

430
00:23:10.800 --> 00:23:11.830
Help!

431
00:23:11.830 --> 00:23:13.070
Help!

432
00:23:13.070 --> 00:23:14.830
