434
00:23:18.800 --> 00:23:20.800
Villain!

435
00:23:20.800 --> 00:23:23.500
Thy own hand yields thydeath's instrument.

436
00:23:25.900 --> 00:23:29.130
Go thou, and fill anotherroom in hell.

437
00:24:00.470 --> 00:24:03.570
