438
00:24:03.570 --> 00:24:06.100
that staggers thus myperson.

439
00:24:09.070 --> 00:24:12.000
Exton, thy fierce hand

440
00:24:12.000 --> 00:24:16.830
hath with the king's bloodstained the king's own land.

441
00:24:16.830 --> 00:24:20.370
Mount; mount, my soul.

442
00:24:20.370 --> 00:24:22.600
Thy seat is up on high,

443
00:24:22.600 --> 00:24:29.400
whilst my gross flesh sinksdownward, here to die.

444
00:24:42.870 --> 00:24:46.270
Kind Uncle York, thelatest news we hear

445
00:24:46.270 --> 00:24:48.200
