451
00:25:04.800 --> 00:25:06.770
But here is Carlisleliving

452
00:25:06.770 --> 00:25:09.930
to abide thy kingly doomand sentence of his pride.

453
00:25:12.570 --> 00:25:14.500
Carlisle, this is your doom.

454
00:25:16.370 --> 00:25:20.400
Choose out some secretplace, some reverend room,

455
00:25:20.400 --> 00:25:23.900
