456
00:25:23.900 --> 00:25:27.330
So as thou livest in peace,die free from strife.

457
00:25:28.330 --> 00:25:30.300
For though mine enemy thouhast ever been,

458
00:25:30.300 --> 00:25:33.670
high sparks of honor inthee have I seen.

459
00:25:52.670 --> 00:25:54.830
Great king,

460
00:25:54.830 --> 00:25:57.430
within this coffin Ipresent thy buried fear.

461
00:25:58.500 --> 00:25:59.930
