463
00:26:05.030 --> 00:26:07.570
Richard of Bordeaux,

464
00:26:07.570 --> 00:26:09.070
by me hither brought.

465
00:26:27.530 --> 00:26:29.500
Exton, I thank thee not,

466
00:26:31.570 --> 00:26:35.770
for thou hast wrought a deedof slander with thy fatal hand

467
00:26:35.770 --> 00:26:39.530
upon my head and all thisfamous land.

468
00:26:39.530 --> 00:26:42.670
