469
00:26:42.670 --> 00:26:45.670
They love not poison thatdo poison need,

470
00:26:45.670 --> 00:26:47.270
nor do I thee.

471
00:26:49.270 --> 00:26:52.400
Though I did wish himdead,

472
00:26:52.400 --> 00:26:53.970
I hate the murderer,

473
00:26:56.430 --> 00:26:57.900
