480
00:27:34.730 --> 00:27:40.200
Come, mourn with me forwhat I do lament,

481
00:27:41.800 --> 00:27:45.130
and put on sullen, blackincontinent.

482
00:27:47.770 --> 00:27:49.730
I'll make a voyage to theHoly Land

483
00:27:49.730 --> 00:27:52.730
to wash this blood fromoff my guilty hand.

484
00:27:54.530 --> 00:27:56.170
March sadly after.

